No other third party receives your Identifying Personal Information or other transactional data, except when you choose to share it with third parties outside our control.
We may share Identifying Personal Information with: Businesses in connection with your direct customer service inquiries and/or requests;
We may share Identifying Personal Information with: Other third parties in limited circumstances, such as reporting suspected criminal activity, complying with legal requirements, preventing fraud, and protecting the safety of our users.
